description: Fidelity Holding Corp., a general holding company, focuses on opportunities in the oil and gas, and renewable energy sectors. The company, through its subsidiary, Rebel Resouces, Inc., engages in the production of heavy oil. It primarily focuses on proprietary thermal technology to extract additional heavy oil out of mature oil fields worldwide. The company was formerly known as Talisman Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Fidelity Holding Corp. in August 2014. Fidelity Holding Corp. was founded in 1998 and is based in Rock Springs, Wyoming.
